          "text" : "Discussion",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Don’t call this initializer directly. Instead, initialize a variable or",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "constant using a string literal with interpolated expressions.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Swift passes this initializer a pair of arguments specifying the size of",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "the literal segments and the number of interpolated segments. Use this",
